      "text": "ん～、気持ちのいい朝ね\n……あら？　怜ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm‚ what a pleasant morning\n…Oh? Rei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.9000000239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
