      "text": "すー……すー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Zzz… zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8000000239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "（昨日、こころちゃん達に付き合って、遅くまで）\n（トランプで遊んでたっけ。そのまま寝ちゃったのね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She was playing cards with Kokoro-chan and the others）\n（until late last night. I guess she fell asleep right here）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0333333572,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13926.6666428
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "（今更起こすのも悪いし）\n（私のスマホで、目覚ましをセットしておこうかしら）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It'd be a shame to wake her up now）\n（Maybe I'll set an alarm on my phone for her）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9333333572,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
