    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、起きて下さい。もう朝ごはん出来てますよ？\n学校の支度もしないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan‚ wake up. Breakfast is ready\nYou need to get ready for school too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.299995955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "んん……だれぇ……ちさぁ……？\nさきぃ……？　んんん……きさぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm… who is it… Chisa-chan…?\nSaki-san…? Mmmmmm… Kisa-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7333333574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "誰ですか、それ。そろそろ起きないと遅刻しますよ\n怜ちゃん、聞いてますかー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who's that? You're going to be late if you don't get up soon\nRei-chan‚ are you listening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "んんー……ぶり……にわりびきぃ……\n……すー……すー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm-m… amberjack… twenty percent off…\n…Zzz… zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5000000241,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15166.666642599992
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十五分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Fifteen minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1333368939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "もぉ沙季！　なんで起こしてくれないのよ！？\n昔はもっと起こしてくれたのに……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ Saki! Why didn't you wake me up!?\nYou used to be much better at waking me up…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "いつまでも甘えないで下さい。もうプロのアイドル\nなんですから。自己管理も仕事のうちです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't be such a baby. You're a professional idol now\nSelf-management is part of the job",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3666671994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かってるけど、今日くらいは……\nどうしよう、駅までタクシー捕まえないと……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I know that‚ but just for today…\nWhat should I do? I'll have to catch a taxi to the station…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8333338661,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14933.334835099999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "朝ごはん、包んでおいたので、お昼に食べて下さいね\nそれじゃあ、行ってきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've packed your breakfast‚ so please eat it at lunch\nWell then‚ I'm heading out",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.5000137571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_04-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "待ってってば～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait for meeeee~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
